<div class="container">
  <article id="workings"> <br> <br>
  <h2>How it Works</h2>
  <p>The budget is just a tool, you do all the spending. This website is built to help make your budgeting a breeze. It also gets you actively involved so you become your own money-manager and be more astute at it with each passing month.</p>
  <p>Once you sign up and sign in, you start with a brand-new budget created just for you. You can customize it, give it a fun name perhaps, describe it or just add your favorite quote when you choose to edit it.</p>
  <p>Also the current month is added for you with two default categories that you can edit according to your preferences as well. Your month is divided into two sections, income (at the top) and expenses (at the bottom). You can also add as many categories as you like to the two sections by clicking on the '+' sign. As you fill out your categories you will see values on page change to reflect your change. If you decide you no longer want a category, just expand it and click the 'Delete' link and it is gone.</p>
  <p>To get you involved, there are four periods that help track your actual income or spending as the month progresses. Mon! will email you periodically, on Sundays, to remind you to update your budget with actual amounts. This exercise is intended to get you actively involved in managing your budget and seeing how well you are doing in your monthly budget, so you can make adjustments as needed.</p>

  <p>If there are features you would like, please contact our team at iwant@mon.com</p>
